### ❌ Items to NOT pursue now

| Item | Reason |
|---|---|
| Full 5-probe ensemble | Over-engineered; fix info flow first |
| Structure cues (additive/multiplicative) | Fragile detection, wrong cues hurt |
| Variable interaction map | Premature for univariate-dominated benchmarks |
